      "text": "WAL 文件结构：\n+------------------------------------------+\n| WAL Header (32 bytes)               |\n|  Magic: 0x377f0682/83              |\n|  Page Size / Checkpoint Seq / Salt|\n|  Checksum-1 / Checksum-2           |\n+------------------------------------------+\n| Frame 1                                  |\n|  +------------------------------------+  |\n|  | Frame Header (24 bytes)       |  |\n|  |  Page Number / Db Size / Salt|  |\n|  |  Checksum-1 / Checksum-2      |  |\n|  +-------------------------------------+  |\n|  | Page Data (page-size bytes)   |  |\n|  +-------------------------------------+  |\n+------------------------------------------+\n| Frame 2  ...                             |\n+------------------------------------------+\n| ...                                         |\n+------------------------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "WAL 文件结构：\n+------------------------------------------+\n| WAL Header (32 bytes)               |\n|  Magic: 0x377f0682/83              |\n|  Page Size / Checkpoint Seq / Salt|\n|  Checksum-1 / Checksum-2           |\n+------------------------------------------+\n| Frame 1                                  |\n|  +------------------------------------+  |\n|  | Frame Header (24 bytes)       |  |\n|  |  Page Number / Db Size / Salt|  |\n|  |  Checksum-1 / Checksum-2      |  |\n|  +-------------------------------------+  |\n|  | Page Data (page-size bytes)   |  |\n|  +-------------------------------------+  |\n+------------------------------------------+\n| Frame 2  ...                             |\n+------------------------------------------+\n| ...                                         |\n+------------------------------------------+",
