      "text": "WAL-Index 结构：\n+---------------------------+\n| WalIndexHdr (header)  | ← 包含 mxFrame / nBackfill / salt\n+---------------------------+\n| Hash Table Block 0    | ← 覆盖 frame 1~4096\n|  Page-Mapping Array   |\n|  Hash Table             |\n+---------------------------+\n| Hash Table Block 1     | ← 覆盖 frame 4097~8192\n|  ...                         |\n+---------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "WAL-Index 结构：\n+---------------------------+\n| WalIndexHdr (header)  | ← 包含 mxFrame / nBackfill / salt\n+---------------------------+\n| Hash Table Block 0    | ← 覆盖 frame 1~4096\n|  Page-Mapping Array   |\n|  Hash Table             |\n+---------------------------+\n| Hash Table Block 1     | ← 覆盖 frame 4097~8192\n|  ...                         |\n+---------------------------+",
